{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Are you constantly struggling with the uncomfortable symptoms of allergies? If so, then you would probably appreciate a wide range of tips to help you deal with the symptoms and the causes. Have you raised a white flag in surrender to your allergies? If you say yes, then this article is the one for you so you can&nbsp;<a href=\"advice-you-need-to-know-if-you-have-allergies\"  >learn a lot about your allergies<\/a>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/stress-woman-holding-her-head.jpg\" class=\"img_left \" alt=\"stress woman holding her head\" style=\"float: left; padding: 8px; padding-left: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Try to avoid becoming too stressed. Believe it or not, something as simple as stress can actually cause allergies to get worse. This is especially true for anyone who is asthmatic. An increased level of stress increases the chance of an <a href=\"http:\/\/www.webmd.com\/asthma\/guide\/asthma-attack\"  >asthma attack<\/a>. Learning to deal with stress in a healthy manner can lower the likelihood of an individual suffering from a severe asthma attack.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Think about removing carpet from your home. Carpet is one of the most notorious places for dust, pollen and dead dust mites to gather. If your house is carpeted, you may want to consider switching to laminate or hardwood floors instead. This will make a big difference when it comes to allergy-causing substances for you to&nbsp;breathe in. Even so, you need to clean your hardwood floors regularly.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/woman-gargling-salt-water.jpg\" class=\"img_right \" alt=\"woman gargling salt water\" style=\"float: right; padding: 8px; padding-right: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Many people use allergy medication but not enough, or in the right way. It is common for such drugs to require consistent use for several days if they are to work well. If you simply take a pill the first time you sneeze, the treatment will not be effective. Make a point to discuss correct usage with your physician.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the symptoms of allergies is called post-nasal drip; if you suffer from sore throats as &nbsp;aresult of this, you can use a salt water gargle for instant relief. Just mix a small amount of warm water with table salt, and&nbsp;gargle with it. Doing so will provide relief for your sore and irritated throat every single time.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Allergies can be a very annoying part of the way the body defends itself. A lot of people do not know what causes their allergies, so they don&#39;t talk about it. If you can learn about why you have allergies, you will be better able to prevent the uncomfortable symptoms.<\/p>\r\n"}